Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:16.12,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年一度的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:17.86,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:22.21,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh 达令　I Love You!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.32,0:22:27.53,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都欢呼雀跃的狂欢节
